#compdef yutu
# Documentation: https://github.com/eat-pray-ai/yutu
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-21
# Verified: upstream docs at the URL above.

# yutu: fully functional CLI for YouTube Data API v3 (cobra-based)
_arguments -s -S \
  '(-h --help)'{-h,--help}'[show help]' \
  '(-v --version)'{-v,--version}'[show version]' \
  '1:command:(auth channel channelBanner channelSection comment commentThread caption thumbnail watermark playlist playlistItem playlistImage video videoCategory videoAbuseReportReason member membershipsLevel subscription search activity superChatEvent i18nLanguage i18nRegion agent mcp completion version help)' \
  '*::arguments:_default'
